title: Islamic State purportedly releases video of raid aftermath
text:
Islamic State purportedly releases video of raid aftermath 
Published By: Boston.com - Today 
The Islamic State group has purportedly released a video showing the aftermath of a raid in northern Iraq by US and Iraqi special forces....
